<section class="pg-section" data-section="What To Expect During Your Rejuvenating Vitamin C Facial Experience">
  <h2 class="pg-h">What To Expect During Your Rejuvenating Vitamin C Facial Experience</h2>
  <p class="pg-text">Every step is designed for relaxation and optimal vitamin C absorption. Here's exactly what happens during your 60-minute treatment at our Millburn spa.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Consultation &amp; Skin Assessment (5-10 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your treatment begins with a thorough consultation to understand your skin concerns and goals. Our expert esthetician analyzes your skin type and condition to customize the vitamin C concentration and treatment approach for your specific needs and sensitivity level.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Your skin is gently cleansed to remove makeup, oils, and environmental pollutants. We prepare your skin for the microdermabrasion treatment, ensuring optimal results from the vitamin C polish and mask that follow.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Professional C Microdermabrasion &amp; Treatment (25-30 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Our signature Professional C microdermabrasion polish gently exfoliates your skin while infusing it with vitamin C. This is followed by a vitamin C mask that deeply penetrates to reveal luminous, radiant skin. You'll enjoy the invigorating citrus aroma as the treatment works to smooth and brighten your complexion.</p>
  <p class="pg-text">Hydration &amp; Protection (10-15 minutes)</p>
  <p class="pg-text">We complete your treatment with hydrating serums and moisturizers that lock in the vitamin C benefits. A broad-spectrum SPF is applied to protect your newly treated skin and maintain your glowing results throughout the day.</p>
  <h3 class="pg-h">Completely Comfortable &amp; Safe</h3>
  <p class="pg-text">This treatment feels like a luxurious, soothing facial massage. There's no discomfort, stinging, or irritation - just pure relaxation while your skin drinks in the powerful antioxidants for an instant healthy glow.</p>
</section>

